@startuml
autonumber
actor "Coordinateur" as Coord
participant "Frontend" as Front
participant "API" as Back
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

title Scénario A : Ouverture des inscriptions (Gestionnaire)

== Initialisation ==
Coord -> Front: Accède à sa formation "Master Big Data"
Front -> Back: GET /api/courses/my-courses/
Back -> DB: SELECT * FROM Course WHERE coordinator_id=...
DB --> Back: Liste des formations
Back --> Front: Affiche les détails

== Modification des dates ==
Coord -> Front: Définit Date Début & Fin + Clic "Ouvrir"
Front -> Back: PATCH /api/courses/{id}/
note right: Payload: { open_date: "2026-03-01", status: "PUBLISHED" }

activate Back
Back -> Back: Vérifie les droits (IsCoordinator)
Back -> DB: UPDATE Course SET ...
DB --> Back: OK
Back --> Front: 200 OK
deactivate Back

Front -> Coord: Notification "Inscriptions ouvertes"
@enduml
